esign and build world\'s best cars.\r\n\r\nCheck out our Bugatti Chiron:\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RdGVz104b3E','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','7-revision-v1','','','2017-08-21 11:03:33','2017-08-21 11:03:33','',7,'http://dev-nigebert-cmp2.pantheonsite.io/2017/08/21/7-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(57,1,'2017-08-21 11:05:36','2017-08-21 11:05:36','<h1>Models</h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nType_101\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nVeyron\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nChiron','Models','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2017-08-21 11:05:36','2017-08-21 11:05:36','',11,'http://dev-nigebert-cmp2.pantheonsite.io/2017/08/21/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(58,1,'2017-08-21 11:07:32','2017-08-21 11:07:32','<h1>Contest</h1>\r\n<h3>Win an all exclusive ride with the new Bugatti Chiron!</h3>\r\nFill in this form to win a ride on the nurburgring with our all new Bugatti Chiron.\r\n\r\nQuestion : How many Bugatti Veyrons have been sold this year.\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"42\" title=\"Contest\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Contest','','inherit','closed','closed','','36-revision-v1','','','2017-08-21 11:07:32','2017-08-21 11:07:32','',36,'http://dev-nigebert-cmp2.pantheonsite.io/2017/08/21/36-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(59,1,'2017-08-21 11:13:56','2017-08-21 11:13:56','A super sports car dream come true. This week, the doors of Bugatti’s “Atelier” at the brand’s headquarters in Molsheim opened for the delivery of the first customer vehicles in the Chiron series. Three of the world’s most powerful, fastest, most luxurious and most exclusive production super sports cars are now starting their journey to their owners in Europe and the Middle East.\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FLyDXO6ra9w\r\n\r\nFuel consumption, l/100km: 35.2 in urban areas / 15.2 in extra urban areas / 22.5 combined; combined CO2 emissions g/km: 516; efficiency class: G','First Chirons leaves the Atelier!','','publish','open','open','','first-chiron-customer-cars-leave-the-bugatti-atelier','','','2017-08-21 11:17:19','2017-08-21 11:17:19','',0,'http://dev-nigebert-cmp2.pantheonsite.io/?p=59',0,'post','',1),(60,1,'2017-08-21 11:13:56','2017-08-21 11:13:56','A super sports car dream come true. This week, the doors of Bugatti’s “Atelier” at the brand’s headquarters in Molsheim opened for the delivery of the first customer vehicles in the Chiron series. Three of the world’s most powerful, fastest, most luxurious and most exclusive production super sports cars are now starting their journey to their owners in Europe and the Middle East.\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FLyDXO6ra9w\r\n\r\nFuel consumption, l/100km: 35.2 in urban areas / 15.2 in extra urban areas / 22.5 combined; combined CO2 emissions g/km: 516; efficiency class: G','First Chiron customer cars leave the Bugatti Atelier!','','inherit','closed','closed','','59-revision-v1','','','2017-08-21 11:13:56','2017-08-21 11:13:56','',59,'http://dev-nigebert-cmp2.pantheonsite.io/2017/08/21/59-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(61,1,'2017-08-21 11:15:01','2017-08-21 11:15:01','Just before deliveries of the Chiron start, Bugatti has requested a real champion to give the French luxury brand’s new ultimate super sports car a final test drive. Football superstar Cristiano Ronaldo, several times World Player of the Year, reigning European Champion, winner of many other awards and a great sports cars fan, got behind the wheel in Madrid to take a close look at the 1,500 PS supercar. His conclusion: approved after comprehensive testing!\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4TAIclkNDwk','The Chiron: Tested and approved','','publish','open','open','','the-bugatti-chiron-tested-and-approved-by-a-champion','','','2017-08-21 11:16:56','2017-08-21 11:16:56','',0,'http://dev-nigebert-cmp2.pantheonsite.io/?p=61',0,'post','',0),(62,1,'2017-08-21 11:15:01','2017-08-21 11:15:01','Just before deliveries of the Chiron start, Bugatti has requested a real champion to give the French luxury brand’s new ultimate supe